    "article": "\n<img alt=\"How To Get Help At Your Local Walk-In Dentists?_1\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists_1.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists_1.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists_1.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists_1.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Need to see a dentist right away? Walk-in dentists are here for you. They offer quick care without needing an appointment. This guide explains what they do and how they can help you with dental emergencies or sudden problems.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 2,
    "title": "How To Get Help At Your Local Walk-In Dentists?",
    "article": "\n<h4>1. Having Severe Pain?</h4>\n<img alt=\"How To Get Help At Your Local Walk-In Dentists?_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content_small/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcostdental.com/Images/content/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists/how-to-get-help-at-your-local-walk-in-dentists_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Got a bad toothache or pain in your mouth? A walk-in dentist can help. They can check your teeth, find out what's wrong, and give you treatment to ease the pain. You don't have to wait for days to get relief.</p>\n</img>"
  },
  {
    "page": 3,
    "title": "How To Get Help At Your Local Walk-In Dentists?",
